{"id": 1961, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心X戴森】是什么阻碍你在冬天活得讲究，而只能将就？", "description": "起床干到爆血，在家也冻得发抖，灯下久坐看书看到四肢僵硬的冬天你还能忍？？反正我是忍不了。", "record_count": 10458, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171017171656EQ54perYWHR2U1qm.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-10-18T03:00:43Z", "options": [{"id": 242433, "content": "穷啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140460}, {"id": 242945, "content": "冷", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1161138}, {"id": 242434, "content": "一年四季都在将就...", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156827}, {"id": 242946, "content": "讲究很重要，生命价更高", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1145813}, {"id": 242435, "content": "从来不将就", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107206}, {"id": 242436, "content": "我喜欢冬天，寒冷算不了什么。享受在瑟瑟发抖的时候更能激发我的潜能，让我奋进。。。。好吧，不扯了，就是因为穷。", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156643}, {"id": 242438, "content": "寂寞", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107202}, {"id": 243206, "content": "len到扎心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 854939}, {"id": 245510, "content": "作业多，一年四季都这样", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1172484}, {"id": 242439, "content": "裹得像个粽子。。。行动不便啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107203}, {"id": 242440, "content": "贫穷限制了我的想象力", "image": null, "praise_count": 74, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215128}, {"id": 242696, "content": "冷 困 穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1153667}, {"id": 242441, "content": "没有供暖，南方女孩在零下的魔都，在家里也穿得像熊，而且瑟瑟发抖", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416515}, {"id": 242442, "content": "是贫穷和懒惰。\n懒惰导致贫穷，贫穷导致活得将就。\n没错，就是这样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1124700}, {"id": 242443, "content": "起不了床！建议人类都应该冬眠", "image": null, "praise_count": 197, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869045}, {"id": 242444, "content": "冷", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1153031}, {"id": 242445, "content": "懒得讲究，冬天熬着熬着就过去了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1106579}, {"id": 242446, "content": "化妆爆皮", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 740151}, {"id": 242447, "content": "冷", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156442}, {"id": 242448, "content": "哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1158601}, {"id": 242449, "content": "哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1158601}, {"id": 242450, "content": "肥", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108190}, {"id": 242451, "content": "穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1011799}, {"id": 242452, "content": "因为没有人可以取暖", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1088307}, {"id": 247828, "content": "冬天衣服太贵了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1177376}, {"id": 242454, "content": "雾霾", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 764743}, {"id": 242455, "content": "魔都人民急需战斗民族的基因", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107204}, {"id": 243223, "content": "湿冷，怎么做都是将就( ´_ゝ`)", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 998348}, {"id": 242456, "content": "早上洗头！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1126574}, {"id": 242457, "content": "电热地暖，电费不堪", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 840856}, {"id": 242459, "content": "因为没有取暖设备，而且身体肌肉少，自己产热不足", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1154007}, {"id": 246555, "content": "舍不得电费呐，终归还是穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225429}, {"id": 242460, "content": "雾霾", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1142352}, {"id": 248604, "content": "没有将就过，从来都是想到什么就去做什么，合理安排生活节奏", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173145}, {"id": 242461, "content": "湿冷的天气加上干燥到爆的皮肤，一边买很多除湿剂在壁橱里，一边加湿器对房间加湿，精分的南方", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 901848}, {"id": 242462, "content": "在宿舍睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1158696}, {"id": 242463, "content": "闷", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1154156}, {"id": 242464, "content": "臃肿而僵硬", "image": null, "praise_count": 107, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 958754}, {"id": 242465, "content": "空间有限，改造困难", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 966798}, {"id": 242466, "content": "用不起戴森的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 220980}, {"id": 243490, "content": "冷", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1096540}, {"id": 242467, "content": "没有男朋友的抱抱，太冷了，如果有男朋友的话，我也会活得讲究", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950816}, {"id": 242468, "content": "穷哩个穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1116257}, {"id": 242469, "content": "懒……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1158744}, {"id": 242470, "content": "我们有供暖。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1158746}, {"id": 242471, "content": "可能是没有男朋友吧就     EM…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1152833}, {"id": 242472, "content": "今天还被习大大点名了最牵挂的还是困难群众。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107407}, {"id": 245544, "content": "南方没暖气", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1172729}, {"id": 242473, "content": "冬天衣服贵", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1155380}, {"id": 242474, "content": "说穷的人加一，要好好挣钱啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108191}]}